Morgion likes green dragons and smells awful. Mother tells me I smell like him after I've played with the hogs in the forest. Paladine doesn't like him.
- Kender Child explaining Krynn mythology</p>
Morgion dwells in Oinos, the first gloom of the Gray Waste, in a Realm called the Fortress of Disease.</p>
Sources: Dragonlance Adventures, Dragonlance Campaign Setting (Third Edition), On Hallowed Ground